OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and patchy rain clearing
OL,6,Faway east this morning. Otherwise it
OL,7,Fwill be mainly dry with bright spells,
OL,8,Falthough a few afternoon showers
OL,9,Fbreaking out later across the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FChance of a few showers this
OL,12,Fevening. Then the rest of the night
OL,13,Fwill be dry with variable cloud and
OL,14,Fsome lengthy clear periods.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FMany places will be dry with
OL,17,Fsome bright intervals, although
OL,18,Fcloudier across western Tayside with a
OL,19,Ffew showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
