OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FScattered showers on Tuesday, slow
OL,7,Fmoving and heavy by afternoon. Drier
OL,8,Fon Wednesday with fewer showers. Early
OL,9,Frain on Thursday then dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
